        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed flex-1">
          Get back to nature and explore the mountains of Crete on a guided Quad Bike tour from Malia. Journey through the stunning views of traditional mountain, seaside villages and the wildlife nature. This off-road track offers great opportunities for amazing photos and breath-taking scenery. Visit an olive oil factory. Before starting your quad tour experience, get acquainted with your ATV vehicle, including lessons for beginners, by an instructor. Begin by going uphill at Omalia Olive Press to reach your first stop, the Malia Port and Potamos Beach, where you will be greeted by impressive views of the surroundings. Continue on the dirt roads to explore the narrow streets of the quaint fishing village of Sisi.
        </p>
